{"title":"战洪灾","authors":["莫文骅"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战洪灾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫文骅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三江狂涛天上来，（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾汹涌百年灾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿树成群随流倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房屋高耸被沉埋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万顷良田变大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛虎搬家另安排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老幼病残多困苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜树抱一孤孩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导带头号令出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民武警行迅速。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同守坝死决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗洪人墙代石木。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露宿更遭风和雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥食冷饭心亦足。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牺牲伤残何足惧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但求大众安骨肉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八方支援一方难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同胞解囊爱心献。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华侨踊跃多捐资，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国际友人亦心善。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"义演巨款当场收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"募捐竞争热场面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活治病灾民营，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府安排不稍乱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪灾损失千千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民经考验。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"危难深觉党英明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾害更促高威望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生我党风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重建家园须苦战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民团结如一人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下无敌肩重担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：即长江、嫩江、松花江。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}